  "detailed_description": "Terminal Breach is a timed survival shooter where you get data experience to level-up and gain upgrades, demolish as much waves of enemies as you can and survive until the timer is complete to successfully breach the terminal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >// GAME CRASHING SYNERGIES</h2>Experiment and play with different playstyles by combining breachers with other item upgrades, bullet modifiers and weapons to unleash countless bullets to your enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/1023ddf38796e7f04b7bd6f7ae9a5354.poster.avif?t=1681398050\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/1023ddf38796e7f04b7bd6f7ae9a5354.webm?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/1023ddf38796e7f04b7bd6f7ae9a5354.mp4?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >// DIVERSE SELECTION OF BREACHERS</h2>Choose a breacher that is fit to your style. They vary stats from each other and have their own strengths and weaknesses, distinct feel and an active ability to aid you in your breach.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/f68b86b9ed4acb1f03dc9b2309b9384e.poster.avif?t=1681398050\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/f68b86b9ed4acb1f03dc9b2309b9384e.webm?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/f68b86b9ed4acb1f03dc9b2309b9384e.mp4?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >// FEATURES FEATURES FEATURES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/71f591bb42e12d8149448055e57317e8.poster.avif?t=1681398050\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/71f591bb42e12d8149448055e57317e8.webm?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/71f591bb42e12d8149448055e57317e8.mp4?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedural map generation to make every run just a little different from the last.<br></li><li>4 Maps are planned to be released in the full version of the game.<br></li><li>20 Unique item modifiers that alter your gunplay.<br></li><li>90 Stackable passive upgrade items to infinitely scale your stats.<br></li><li>30 Playable breachers with their own playstyle and ability.<br></li><li>25 Permanent upgrades you can invest in your breacher for further progression.<br></li><li>60 Varied weapons in your arsenal. (pistols, smg's, shotgun, assault rifle, sniper rifle, throwers, repeaters and launchers)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Terminal Breach is a timed survival shooter where you get data experience to level-up and gain upgrades, demolish as much waves of enemies as you can and survive until the timer is complete to successfully breach the terminal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >// GAME CRASHING SYNERGIES</h2>Experiment and play with different playstyles by combining breachers with other item upgrades, bullet modifiers and weapons to unleash countless bullets to your enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/1023ddf38796e7f04b7bd6f7ae9a5354.poster.avif?t=1681398050\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/1023ddf38796e7f04b7bd6f7ae9a5354.webm?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/1023ddf38796e7f04b7bd6f7ae9a5354.mp4?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >// DIVERSE SELECTION OF BREACHERS</h2>Choose a breacher that is fit to your style. They vary stats from each other and have their own strengths and weaknesses, distinct feel and an active ability to aid you in your breach.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/f68b86b9ed4acb1f03dc9b2309b9384e.poster.avif?t=1681398050\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/f68b86b9ed4acb1f03dc9b2309b9384e.webm?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/f68b86b9ed4acb1f03dc9b2309b9384e.mp4?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >// FEATURES FEATURES FEATURES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/71f591bb42e12d8149448055e57317e8.poster.avif?t=1681398050\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/71f591bb42e12d8149448055e57317e8.webm?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111590/extras/71f591bb42e12d8149448055e57317e8.mp4?t=1681398050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedural map generation to make every run just a little different from the last.<br></li><li>4 Maps are planned to be released in the full version of the game.<br></li><li>20 Unique item modifiers that alter your gunplay.<br></li><li>90 Stackable passive upgrade items to infinitely scale your stats.<br></li><li>30 Playable breachers with their own playstyle and ability.<br></li><li>25 Permanent upgrades you can invest in your breacher for further progression.<br></li><li>60 Varied weapons in your arsenal. (pistols, smg's, shotgun, assault rifle, sniper rifle, throwers, repeaters and launchers)</li></ul>",
